#: source/nijigenerate/widgets/mainmenu.d:240
msgid "Puppet Data"
msgstr "模型資料"

#: source/nijigenerate/widgets/mainmenu.d:245
msgid ""
"Imports tracking data from an exported nijilive model which has been set up "
"in Inochi Session."
msgstr "匯入已在 Inochi Session 中設定的匯出 nijilive 模型追蹤資料。"

#: source/nijigenerate/widgets/mainmenu.d:248
msgid "Puppet Texturing"
msgstr "模型材質"

#: source/nijigenerate/widgets/mainmenu.d:254
msgid ""
"Premultiplies textures by their alpha component.\n"
"\n"
"Only use this if your textures look garbled after importing files from an "
"older version of nijigenerate."
msgstr ""
"將材質預先乘上 Alpha 分量。\n"
"\n"
"僅在從舊版 nijigenerate 匯入檔案後材質顯示異常時使用。"

#: source/nijigenerate/widgets/mainmenu.d:257
msgid ""
"Causes color to bleed out in to fully transparent pixels, this solves "
"outlines on straight alpha compositing.\n"
"\n"
"Only use this if your game engine can't use premultiplied alpha."
msgstr ""
"使色彩滲出到透明像素上，以消除直通 alpha 渲染的白邊.\n"
"\n"
"僅適用於不支援預乘 alpha 的遊戲引擎."

#: source/nijigenerate/widgets/mainmenu.d:260
msgid "Regenerates the puppet's mipmaps."
msgstr "重新生成模型 Mipmaps。"

#: source/nijigenerate/widgets/mainmenu.d:263
msgid "Generates fake layer info based on node names"
msgstr "依據節點名稱產生假圖層資訊"

#: source/nijigenerate/widgets/mainmenu.d:269
msgid "Puppet Recovery"
msgstr "模型修復"

#: source/nijigenerate/widgets/mainmenu.d:274
msgid ""
"Attempts all the recovery and repair methods below on the currently loaded "
"model"
msgstr "對當前模型進行以下所有修復方式"

#: source/nijigenerate/widgets/mainmenu.d:278
msgid "Regenerates all the unique IDs for the model"
msgstr "重新生成模型獨特 ID"

#: source/nijigenerate/widgets/mainmenu.d:285
msgid "Attempts to verify and repair INP files"
msgstr "嘗試驗證和修復 INP 檔"

#: source/nijigenerate/widgets/mainmenu.d:290
msgid "Help"
msgstr "幫助"

#: source/nijigenerate/widgets/mainmenu.d:292
msgid "Online Documentation"
msgstr "線上說明書"

#: source/nijigenerate/widgets/mainmenu.d:296
msgid "nijilive Documentation"
msgstr "nijilive 說明書"

#: source/nijigenerate/widgets/mainmenu.d:304
