#: source/app.d:162
msgid ""
"You're running a nightly build of nijigenerate!\n"
"nijigenerate may crash unexpectedly and you will likely encounter bugs.\n"
"Make sure to save and back up your work often!"
msgstr ""
"You're running a nightly build nijigenerate!\n"
"nijigenerate may crash unexpectedly you will likely encounter bugs.\n"
"Make sure save back up your work often!"

